%Docstring
Called when the widget's algorithm should be run. Must be overridden by
subclasses.
%End

    virtual void algExecuted( bool successful, const QVariantMap &results );
%Docstring
Called when an algorithm task has completed.

.. versionadded:: 3.26
%End

